        &kp LSHFT &kp Z      &kp X      &kp C       &kp V       &kp B                            &none    &none                    &kp N  &kp M       &kp COMMA   &kp DOT    &kp FSLH      &kp RSHFT
        &none     &kp GRAVE  &none      &none       &none                    &kp SPACE &mo L_SYM &none    &none  &mo L_SYM &kp BSPC       &kp ENTER   &kp MINUS   &none      &none         &none
